cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper is about investigating potential issues in Q-learning with function approximation, which is a common problem in reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also deals with nonstationarity and control domains, which are related to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), respectively.
